snippet.title: Best VGM 1227 - Superbrothers : Sword & Sworcery EP - Lone Star
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1059 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hB3mYnW-v4w

Buy the soundtrack here : http://jimguthrie.bandcamp.com/album/sword-sworcery-lp-the-ballad-of-the-space-babies

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

iOS / PC
Lone Star
Jim Guthrie
